{"tid":87030,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥斯尼盛讚雲格：佢唔止教踢波 還教做人","createTime":"2017-01-19T13:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T15:49:36.000Z","uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce333b0fcf51a77e398aacf9475202ac0c8bfb2d","tid":87030,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"　阿仙奴大將哥斯尼近期剛和球隊完成了續約，在他看來，雲格就是他決定留隊的最大原因。雲格不僅幫助球員成長，也幫助他們成長為更好的人。<br />\n<br />\n　　哥斯尼說：「你們可以說阿仙奴很久沒有拿到冠軍了，但是雲格不只是在培養球員，他還在幫助球員成長為更好的人。每個為阿仙奴效力的球員都得到了成長，變成了一個更好的人。對我和其他人來說，和雲格在一起，向他學習都是一個很好的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「雲格總是對足球充滿熱情，他愛足球，喜歡看到他的球隊出色的控球，那就是他在這裡堅守20年的原因。他幫助球會建立了新的球場，他讓我們每一年都能競爭英超和歐冠盃。」"},{"pid":"816e52ccb77176875899031ba848f6344cb8f4d6","tid":87030,"uid":41733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"電叻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0e7a4287b505fbb21ecddbffdbb09e6ffcf0bb","tid":87030,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b51599e4a9b634470a79578b49ffd54b54399f9","tid":87030,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"暈加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0d80a0760ac46e24e8615ac5d92fbba139f669","tid":87030,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"還教各位做愛<br />\n教韋拉露械"},{"pid":"ed9f22580d36aecf8ac3820e2c05beff0699e6c2","tid":87030,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:10:10.000Z","msg":"雲加又贏"},{"pid":"0741cee9fbed544ee3b0ea5c9be9ddc4d68c0a15","tid":87030,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"他讓我們每一年都能競爭英超和歐冠盃<br />\n<br />\n有得爭冇得拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma